<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/index.css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@100&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body >
    @* <div id="loading-screen">
        <div class="loading-text">Loading...</div>
    </div> *@
    <div id="zoom-texts">
        <div id="zoom-text-addstud">
            <h1 class="zoom-text-h1">Enroll a New Student</h1>
            <h2 class="zoom-text-h2" style="text-indent: .5em;">Welcome New Faces to Our School</h2>
            <p class="zoom-text-p" style="text-indent: 3em;">
                Adding a new student to our school community is the first step toward unlocking a world of opportunities for their growth and development.
                Click the button below to begin the enrollment process and help shape their educational journey.
            </p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Add", "Students")" class="btn-in-zoom">ENROLL NOW</a>
        </div>
        <div id="zoom-text-students">
            <h1 class="zoom-text-h1">Student Directory</h1>
            <h2 class="zoom-text-h2" style="margin: 2% 0;">Explore Student Profiles</h2>
            <p class="zoom-text-p">Browse through the list of students currently enrolled in the program. Get insights into their academic progress and personal details.</p>
            <p class="zoom-text-p" style=" width:80%; margin-left: auto; margin-top: -1.3%;">View the profiles of our students and track their achievements and activities.</p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("List", "Students")" class="btn-in-zoom">VIEW STUDENTS</a>
        </div>
        <div id="zoom-text-addsub">
            <h1 class="zoom-text-h1">Add a New Subject Today</h1>
            <h2 class="zoom-text-h2" style="text-indent: .5em;">Expand Your Curriculum—Create Your Unique Course Offerings</h2>
            <p class="zoom-text-p" style="text-indent: 3em;">
                Whether you’re developing a new program, responding to student needs, or innovating your educational offerings, our platform provides all the tools you need to add a subject.
                Start the process today to enrich your academic catalog.
            </p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Add", "Subjects")" class="btn-in-zoom">ADD YOUR SUBJECT</a>
        </div>
        <div id="zoom-text-addsched">
            <h1 class="zoom-text-h1">Assign Schedules Effeciently</h1>
            <h2 class="zoom-text-h2" style="text-indent: .5em;">Organize Your Classes—Manage Course Timetables Effectively</h2>
            <p class="zoom-text-p" style="text-indent: 3em;">
                Streamline your educational offerings by efficiently assigning schedules for your subjects. Whether you're optimizing class times or accommodating student needs, our platform makes it easy to manage your course schedules.
                Begin the scheduling process today to enhance your academic planning.
            </p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Add", "SubjectSchedules")" class="btn-in-zoom">ASSIGN YOUR SCHEDULES</a>
        </div>
        <div id="zoom-text-subjects">
            <h1 class="zoom-text-h1">Subject Listings</h1>
            <h2 class="zoom-text-h2" style="text-indent: .5em;">Explore Available Courses and Find What Interests You</h2>
            <p class="zoom-text-p" style="text-indent: 3em;">
                Discover a comprehensive list of all available subjects offered. Whether you’re looking to enroll in a new course or explore different fields of study, our platform provides easy access to detailed subject information.
                Start browsing our offerings today to find the right subjects for your academic journey.
            </p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("List", "Subjects")" class="btn-in-zoom">VIEW SUBJECT LIST</a>
        </div>
        <div id="zoom-text-schedules">
            <h1 class="zoom-text-h1">View All Schedules</h1>
            <h2 class="zoom-text-h2" style="text-indent: .5em;">Manage Your Class Timetables, Always Stay Organized</h2>
            <p class="zoom-text-p" style="text-indent: 3em;">
                Access a complete list of all assigned schedules for your subjects. Whether you're reviewing class times or ensuring compliance with scheduling requirements, our platform makes it easy to stay informed.
                Check your schedules today to ensure you’re on track for a successful academic term.
            </p>
            <a href="@Url.Action("List", "SubjectSchedules")" class="btn-in-zoom">VIEW SCHEDULE LIST</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="caption">
        Your academic hub | Connect with resources, manage your studies, and stay on top of important updates.
    </div>
    <div class="close-btn">Back</div>
    <div class="track-container">
        <div class="left-icon">
            <input type="checkbox" id="left-icon-checkbox" style="display:none;">
            <label for="left-icon-checkbox">
                <img width="50" height="50" src="https://imgur.com/wcdMngb.png" alt="Icon" draggable="false" />
            </label>
            
        </div>
        <div class="right-icon">
            <input type="checkbox" id="right-icon-checkbox" style="display:none;">
            <label for="right-icon-checkbox">
                <img width="50" height="50" src="https://imgur.com/w38T1bk.png" alt="double-right" draggable="false" />
            </label>
        </div>
        <div class="center-icon">
            <img width="45" height="45" src="https://imgur.com/B6SIXrn.png" alt="external-Drag-hand-gestures-on-ipad-outline-berkahicon" />
        </div>
        <div id="image-track" data-mouse-down-at="0" data-prev-percentage="0">
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-addstud" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://imgur.com/8RIDUwi.jpeg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-students" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://mycehd.gsu.edu/files/2020/10/research-diverse-students-planning-banner-1920x1080.jpg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-addsub" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://i.abcnewsfe.com/a/58a35e3a-b15c-46f4-8bb3-a71ccf9809d0/ca-schools-3-rf-gty-bb-230906_1694023890660_hpMain.jpg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-addsched" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://www.daysoftheyear.com/wp-content/uploads/world-student-day1.jpg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-subjects" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://imgur.com/vq5JpUu.jpeg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-schedules" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://imgur.com/72UcVFH.jpeg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-addstud" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://imgur.com/qVVxlqP.jpeg" draggable="false">
            </label>
            <label>
                <input type="checkbox" class="image-checkbox" data-zoom-text="zoom-text-addstud" style="display:none;">
                <img class="image" src="https://www.universityliving.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Student-Library-Top-Pick-Books-For-Students-to-Read-1000x418.webp" draggable="false">
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>
   
    <div class="intro-section">
        <div class="intro-texts">
            <h1>WELCOME TO YOUR STUDENT PORTAL</h1>
            <h2>Effortlessly Manage Student Enrollments and Courses</h2>
            <p>Streamline subject enrollment, profile management, and academic tracking for students and administrators.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-btn">

            <input type="hidden" id="IsAuthenticated" value="@User.Identity.IsAuthenticated">
            <button class="intro-btn1">LEARN MORE</button>
            @if (!User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
            {
                <button class="intro-btn2" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Signup", "Home")'" type="button">GET STARTED</button>
            }
            else
            {
                <button class="intro-btn2">GET STARTED</button>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="featured-section">
        <h1>Designed for Your Convenience</h1>
        <div class="image-container">
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://imgur.com/7VQl6uj.png" alt="map" />
                <p class="head-description">Easy Navigation</p>
                <p class="sub-description">Find what you need effortlessly with straightforward</p>
                <p class="sub-description">and logical navigation options.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://imgur.com/u0eqaGM.png" alt="checked--v1" />
                <p class="head-description">Seamless Enrollment</p>
                <p class="sub-description">Enroll students quickly with an intuitive, step-by-step enrollment</p>
                <p class="sub-description">process that simplifies registration and setup.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://imgur.com/L5vRilk.png" alt="folder-invoices" />
                <p class="head-description">Quick Access to Resources</p>
                <p class="sub-description">Instantly retrieve important documents</p>
                <p class="sub-description">links, and tools without hassle.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://imgur.com/mw9qUZv.png" alt="apple-clock" />
                <p class="head-description">Real-Time Updates</p>
                <p class="sub-description">Stay informed with up-to-the-minute</p>
                <p class="sub-description">notifications and content refreshes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-column">
                <img src="https://imgur.com/BOtoaQY.png" alt="automatic" />
                <p class="head-description">Personalized Settings</p>
                <p class="sub-description">Adjust your preferences and settings to match</p>
                <p class="sub-description">your individual needs and working style.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
